{"tid":2083402,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"李遐怡街頭演唱鐘鉉遺作！「你真的辛苦了」路人聽哭頻擦淚","createTime":"2020-06-28T16:57:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T22:52:16.000Z","uid":74065,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d16e62f1542f9740c124b43f8db500d2945e4253","tid":2083402,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T16:57:34.000Z","msg":"南韓已故藝人鐘鉉生前曾為女歌手李遐怡（LEE HI）寫過《Breathe（한숨）》，從歌詞可看出當時他壓抑的心境，遐怡曾在對方過世隔年於頒獎典禮獻唱時，還一度哽咽唱不下去。她最近上節目在街頭演唱此首歌曲，溫暖的嗓音唱著「你真的辛苦了」感動路人，讓台下觀眾不禁頻頻拭淚。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4968/d4968142.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4968%2Fd4968142.jpg&h=1b4ef392&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲李遐怡街頭演唱鐘鉉遺作。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／Beginagain 비긴어게인）<br />\n<br />\n南韓綜藝節目《Begin Again》主題是找來歌手與樂手，到街頭進行快閃演唱，之前都在國外的他們，最新一季因為疫情關係則選擇在南韓國內，而第4集加入了新成員，就是曾是YG娛樂旗下solo女歌手的李遐怡。<br />\n<br />\n他們來到海邊，在船上舉辦臨時演唱會，邀請路人席地觀賞，李遐怡與男歌手鄭承煥合唱她的招牌歌曲之一《Breathe》，一開始由女生先唱，接著換男生，兩人明明年紀超輕，卻擁有歷經滄桑的感性嗓音，這首歌曲的歌詞希望被壓力壓得喘不過氣的人們，能夠透過此曲獲得安慰與釋放，在結束時最後一句歌詞是「你真的辛苦了」，讓不少觀眾當場聽完落淚。.<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4968/d4968143.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4968%2Fd4968143.jpg&h=d7e4f30c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲許多路人聽完此曲頻擦淚。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／Beginagain 비긴어게인）<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，曾經是同公司的李遐怡與樂童音樂家李秀賢，也一起合唱了6年前曾一起組成「HI SUHYUN」，當時推出的輕快主打歌《나는 달라(I'M DIFFERENT)》，讓許多歌迷都十分懷念。<br />\n<br />\n▼李遐怡與鄭承煥演唱《Breathe》。（影片來源：YouTube Beginagain 비긴어게인）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uzscBqOanuo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuzscBqOanuo&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8YhgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=ecc24c68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uzscBqOanuo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />BREATHE每次睇STAGE都忍唔住喊"},{"pid":"173e392ce410691c539df794baa8f8b4ca5df40a","tid":2083402,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T17:00:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n_CeY6DJVi0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dn_CeY6DJVi0&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8YhgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=66900022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n_CeY6DJVi0</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b98516e5f79b056a847a40b21c75ea5de424d65","tid":2083402,"uid":307619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T17:19:20.000Z","msg":"希望佢喺天上過得快樂"},{"pid":"eb89e3a917ff02a761ca720f90ce4dcc1579a26b","tid":2083402,"uid":25924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T17:20:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aec9157bbe1e27e393c1170f4225fe04d03861c","tid":2083402,"uid":81725,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T17:28:25.000Z","msg":"樓豬比人hack ac？？？<br />\n平時一向出開垃圾post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4471652b588cac9ca17e1991c1ce163c71ab01c","tid":2083402,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6aec9157bbe1e27e393c1170f4225fe04d03861c","tid":2083402,"uid":81725,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T17:28:25.000Z","msg":"樓豬比人hack ac？？？<br />\n平時一向出開垃圾post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T17:47:40.000Z","msg":"我不嬲吹奏開LEEHI"},{"pid":"148c674323088a399ed4ab72b2e8298f2621fc44","tid":2083402,"uid":52073,"like"